:GRAPH WORLD
:TITLE World Model Results
:X-DIV 7
:WIDTH 25
:HEIGHT 15
:SCALE
:VAR Population
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 4
:SCALE
:VAR Capital
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:SCALE
:VAR Pollution
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:SCALE
:VAR Natural Resources
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:SCALE
:VAR quality of life
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 2

:GRAPH GRAPH1_DOTS
:TITLE Results from the WORLD model.
:X-DIV 7
:WIDTH 25
:HEIGHT 15
:DOTS
:SCALE
:VAR Capital
:DATASET 
:SHAPE CIRCLE,3
:SCALE
:VAR Natural_Resources
:DATASET 
:SHAPE X,2
:SCALE
:VAR quality_of_life
:DATASET 
:SHAPE CROSS,2
:SCALE
:VAR Population
:DATASET 
:SHAPE DIAMOND,2
:SCALE
:VAR Pollution
:DATASET 
:SHAPE TRIANGLE,3

:GRAPH Population_Drivers
:TITLE Population Drivers
:SCALE
:VAR food ratio
:DATASET 
:VAR crowding
:DATASET 
:VAR material standard of living
:DATASET 
:VAR pollution ratio
:DATASET 

:GRAPH Population-Material_Std
:TITLE Population - Material Standard
:X-AXIS material standard of living
:SCALE
:VAR births material multiplier
:DATASET 
:VAR deaths material multiplier
:DATASET 

:GRAPH Birth_&_Death_Rates
:TITLE Birth & Death Rates
:SCALE
:VAR birth rate
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 3
:VAR death rate
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 3
:SCALE
:VAR food ratio
:DATASET 
:LINE-WIDTH 1
:VAR pollution ratio
:DATASET 
:LINE-STYLE DASH
:VAR material standard of living
:DATASET 
:LINE-STYLE DOT

:GRAPH Population_-_Food
:TITLE Population - Food
:X-AXIS food ratio
:X-MIN 0
:SCALE
:VAR births food multiplier
:Y-MIN 0
:DATASET 
:VAR deaths food multiplier
:DATASET 

:GRAPH Population_-_Pollution
:TITLE Population - Pollution
:X-AXIS Population
:DOTS
:SCALE
:VAR Pollution
:DATASET 
